{"tid":1142763,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女師傅幫大家占塔羅！","createTime":"2019-05-07T09:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T11:04:24.000Z","uid":62507,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"29d8cb12570ec0afa5b252dc7e14230786697037","tid":1142763,"uid":62507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"大家好，我叫女師傅，幫大家占下塔羅（其實係自己超迷戀幫人占<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n呢個AC係我同男師傅一齊用<br />\n男師傅就專長中式野，睇掌相紫微斗數<br />\n女師傅就專長西式野，星座塔羅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過今次就女師傅負責，塔羅問卜<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n問題背景最好愈詳細愈好，時間愈近期愈好<br />\n<br />\n感情問題<br />\n例如<br />\n同A咩關係，識左幾耐，想點樣<br />\n同A拍拖左一段時間，佢想分手，可以點<br />\n同A拍拖左一段時間，有第三介入，點好<br />\n<br />\n學業事業問題<br />\n例如<br />\nDSE結果如何<br />\nDSE預左炒粉，想問升學應該讀i大好？<br />\n有份新工請我，但舊工又好pay，做新工好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n其他問題都ok<br />\n<br />\n如果太私隱既野，你可以ig pm問我地（請注明搵男師傅定女師傅）<br />\n<br />\n我得閒就會響度出下post，如果無覆就下次睇緣份喇！因為要湊BB，會成日都無時間<br />\n<br />\n我同男師傅會響ig同fb不定期post 星相問卜既野，你有性趣就follow啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nig:YourFaceYourFateHK<br />\nfb:Your Face Your Fate"},{"pid":"eae83f319e6f43522643978365542c623e0f7684","tid":1142763,"uid":40470,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母2019年仲有d迷信撚<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},{"pid":"d0ba95b302802617a8a7be09444469a09b8b722d","tid":1142763,"uid":241967,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8c258d452bdb3419d2c58bebdfe5618c4ce959","tid":1142763,"uid":183025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7223d364fe8ce6b21b324ad3cc2d94974c9b89a0","tid":1142763,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"事業，做工程，幾時先轉到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"